ation), use combination code E11.40 when the specific type of neuropathy is not documented.", "source": "ICD-10-CM Guidelines", "section": "Chapter 4 - Diabetes"}]}, {"code": "E11.65", "role": "secondary", "sequence": 2, "modifiers": [], "_agreement": 1.0, "confidence": 0.9, "code_system": "ICD10CM", "description": "Type 2 diabetes mellitus with hyperglycemia", "chart_citations": [{"text": "Blood sugars running high at home.", "section": "HPI", "line_end": 2, "line_start": 2}, {"text": "A1C resulted today at 9.2%.", "section": "DATA", "line_end": 6, "line_start": 6}, {"text": "Type 2 diabetes mellitus, uncontrolled — increase metformin", "section": "ASSESSMENT/PLAN", "line_end": 7, "line_start": 7}], "rule_justification": "Documented high home blood sugars and A1C of 9.2% (>7% target) with uncontrolled diabetes supports coding hyperglycemia.", "guideline_citations": [{"text": "Code E11.65 is used when type 2 diabetes is documented with hyperglycemia. An A1C >7% with documented high blood sugars supports hyperglycemia.", "source": "ICD-10-CM Guidelines", "section": "Chapter 4 - Diabetes"}]}, {"code": "I10", "role": "secondary", "sequence": 3, "modifiers": [], "_agreement": 1.0, "confidence": 0.95, "code_system": "ICD10CM", "description": "Essential (primary) hypertension", "chart_citations": [{"text": "Lisinopril 10 mg daily.", "section": "MEDICATIONS", "line_end": 4, "line_start": 4}, {"text": "Hypertension — stable, continue lisinopril.", "section": "ASSESSMENT/PLAN", "line_end": 7, "line_start": 7}], "rule_justification": "Hypertension documented as stable condition being treated with lisinopril; no indication of secondary hypertension.", "guideline_citations": [{"text": "Code I10 is assigned for essential hypertension when the type is not specified as secondary.", "source": "ICD-10-CM Guidelines", "section": "Chapter 9 - Circulatory System"}]}, {"code": "99214", "role": "procedure", "sequence": 4, "modifiers": [], "_agreement": 1.0, "confidence": 0.9, "code_system": "CPT", "description": "Office/outpatient visit, established patient, moderate MDM", "chart_citations": [{"text": "OFFICE VISIT NOTE (Established Patient)", "section": "OFFICE VISIT NOTE", "line_end": 1, "line_start": 1}, {"text": "1) Type 2 diabetes mellitus, uncontrolled — increase metformin, discussed diet. 2) Hypertension — stable, continue lisinopril. Total time 35 minutes.", "section": "ASSESSMENT/PLAN", "line_end": 7, "line_start": 7}], "rule_justification": "Moderate MDM met: 2 stable chronic + 1 uncontrolled chronic problem, lab review, prescription management; 35 minutes total time also supports 99214.", "guideline_citations": [{"text": "99214 requires moderate MDM (2 stable chronic + 1 uncontrolled chronic problem, minimal data, prescription drug management) OR 30-39 minutes total time for established patients.", "source": "CPT E/M Guidelines 2021+", "section": "Office/Outpatient E/M"}]}]}, {"stage": "3b_citation", "title": "Citation Verification", "verified": [{"ok": true, "code": "E11.40", "score": 1.0}, {"ok": true, "code": "E11.65", "score": 1.0}, {"ok": true, "code": "I10", "score": 1.0}, {"ok": true, "code": "99214", "score": 1.0}]}, {"stage": "4_validation", "title": "Validation & Compliance Gates", "results": [{"code": "E11.40", "gates": [{"gate": "code_existence", "detail": "E11.40 valid for DOS 2026-04-16", "passed": true}, {"gate": "specificity", "detail": "most-specific billable code", "passed": true}, {"gate": "sex_edit", "detail": "", "passed": true}, {"gate": "age_edit", "detail": "", "passed": true}], "status": "accepted", "citation_score": 1.0, "citation_verified": true}, {"code": "E11.65", "gates": [{"gate": "code_existence", "detail": "E11.65 valid for DOS 2026-04-16", "passed": true}, {"gate": "specificity", "detail": "most-specific billable code", "passed": true}, {"gate": "sex_edit", "detail": "", "passed": true}, {"gate": "age_edit", "detail": "", "passed": true}], "status": "accepted", "citation_score": 1.0, "citation_verified":